theorem Topology.closure_interior_iter_six_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior (closure (interior
      (closure (interior (closure (interior
        (closure (interior (closure (interior (A : Set X))))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  -- Collapse the five‐fold iteration using the existing lemma.
  have h₅ :=
    Topology.closure_interior_iter_five_eq (X := X) (A := A)
  -- Rewrite and finish with the idempotence lemma.
  simpa [h₅,
        (Topology.closure_interior_closure_interior_eq (X := X) (A := A))]

theorem Topology.interior_inter_subset_left {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B : Set X} :
    interior (A ∩ B : Set X) ⊆ interior A := by
  exact interior_mono (Set.inter_subset_left : (A ∩ B : Set X) ⊆ A)
